data.title: David Fisher, former Representative for Ohio's 2nd Congressional District
data.meta_description: Legislative profile for Rep. David Fisher [W-OH2, 1847-1849], the former Representative from Ohio
data.text:
Voting Record

Missed Votes

From Dec 1847 to Mar 1849, Fisher missed 57 of 478 roll call votes, which is 11.9%. This is better than the median of 24.5% among the lifetime records of representatives serving in Mar 1849. The chart below reports missed votes over time.

We don’t track why legislators miss votes, but it’s often due to medical absenses, major life events, and running for higher office.
